# TwitterEggs Tower
TwitterEggs are among the earliest NFTs in blockchain history. They exist on Namecoin, the first fork of Bitcoin. Some early crypto users made use of an app called Onename to lock their profiles into the blockchain forever. In total less than 300 Eggs were created. They are one of the first profile picture NFT collectibles. Not associated with Twitter Inc.
